        "uzbek": "Pul katta dasta edi!",
        "english": "The money was a big bundle!"
      },
      {
        "uzbek": "Men pulni sanadim va xursand bo'ldim.",
        "english": "I counted the money and was happy."
      },
      {
        "uzbek": "Endi men osh va sovg'a sotib olaman.",
        "english": "Now I will buy plov and gifts."
      }
